description-of-drawings.p: FIG. 1 is a front upper perspective view of a helmet of the present disclosure showing our new design;
FIG. 2 is a rear lower perspective view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a first side view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a second side view thereof opposite that shown in FIG. 4;
FIG. 6 is a rear view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a top view thereof; and,
FIG. 8 is a bottom view thereof.
The broken lines in the drawings illustrate features of the helmet that form no part of the claimed design.

claim.claim-text: The ornamental design for a helmet, as shown and described.
